<section id="travel-form" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-wine-dark via-wine to-wine-light text-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <p class="font-display italic text-gold-light text-lg mb-2">Help us plan</p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold">Travel Form</h2>
    <p class="ornament text-gold/50 text-sm mt-4 mb-8">&mdash; &#10049; &mdash;</p>
    <p class="text-cream/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Please fill out the travel form so we can coordinate airport and station transfers,
      match drivers with riders, and plan for dietary needs.
    </p>
    <p class="text-cream/60 mb-10">
      Even if your plans aren&rsquo;t final yet, a rough idea helps us enormously.
      You can always update your response later.
    </p>

    <a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfE0bd3SXMPX5bJj5PL-jqzyflM-uuAhxujQYcCCLNH07ZXQg/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
       class="inline-block bg-gold hover:bg-gold-dark text-white font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors text-lg uppercase tracking-wider shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
      Open the Travel Form
    </a>

    <div class="mt-12 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-5">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-gold-light mb-2">What we&rsquo;ll ask</h4>
        <ul class="text-sm text-cream/70 space-y-1">
          <li>&#8226; Your arrival &amp; departure dates</li>
          <li>&#8226; How you&rsquo;re travelling</li>
          <li>&#8226; Whether you need a transfer</li>
          <li>&#8226; If you can offer spare car seats</li>
          <li>&#8226; Dietary needs &amp; allergies</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-5">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-gold-light mb-2">Deadline</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-cream/70">
          Please submit by <strong class="text-white">mid-June 2026</strong> so we can
          organise the logistics. The sooner the better!
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-5">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-gold-light mb-2">Questions?</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-cream/70">
          Reach out on the WhatsApp group or email us directly.
          We&rsquo;re happy to help with travel planning.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
